Accommodation
<h2>Accommodation</h2>

<p>Cambridge offers a variety of hotels, B&amp;Bs and travel lodges. More information can be found on <a href="http://www.visitcambridge.org/accommodation">www.visitcambridge.org</a>.

<p>Guests may also stay overnight on Saturday 21st September at Homerton College, which has single rooms available. Details and booking may be found <a href="http://www.homertonconference.com/bedandbreakfast.html">on Homerton's website</a> using the following promotional code "KX 13015". Please note that this is bed-only.</p>